## 生成自签名证书
## 1) 创建证书库
```shell
keytool -genkey -alias local -keyalg RSA -keysize 1024 -validity 365 -keystore local.jks
```
### 1.1) 直接加密码
```shell
keytool -genkey -alias local -keypass 123456 -keyalg RSA -keysize 1024 -validity 365 -keystore local.jks -storepass 123456
```
## 2) 导出证书
```shell
keytool -export -alias local -keystore local.jks -rfc -file local.cer
```
## 3) 导出私钥 (因为keytool不提供命令导出私钥，所以需要编写java类导出key)

import java.io.FileInputStream;
import java.security.KeyStore;
import java.security.PrivateKey;

import sun.misc.BASE64Encoder;

public class Test {

    public static KeyStore getKeyStore(String keyStorePath, String password) throws Exception {
        FileInputStream is = new FileInputStream(keyStorePath);
        KeyStore ks = KeyStore.getInstance("JKS");
        ks.load(is, password.toCharArray());
        is.close();
        return ks;
    }

    public static PrivateKey getPrivateKey() {
        try {
            BASE64Encoder encoder = new BASE64Encoder();
            KeyStore ks = getKeyStore("local.jks", "123456"); // 密钥库, 密码
            PrivateKey key = (PrivateKey) ks.getKey("local", "123456".toCharArray()); // 密钥key, 密码
            String encoded = encoder.encode(key.getEncoded());
            System.out.println("-----BEGIN RSA PRIVATE KEY-----");
            System.out.println(encoded);
            System.out.println("-----END RSA PRIVATE KEY-----");
            return key;
        } catch (Exception e) {
            return null;
        }
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        getPrivateKey();
    }

}
